qxMPgRVpdM</a><br />\n記者に催涙ガスを撃つ香港警察 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/EVyFvdPfkho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEVyFvdPfkho&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=87f75968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EVyFvdPfkho</a><br />\nペッパースプレーでオフィスワーカーを攻撃する香港警察 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/M8CdYFpOMRY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM8CdYFpOMRY&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=259ad3c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M8CdYFpOMRY</a><br />\n香港警察が電車の乗客を攻撃 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/fc69bjT3ROk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ffc69bjT3ROk&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=b5dd799e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fc69bjT3ROk</a><br />\n香港警察がエスカレーターに市民を押し込む <a href=\"https://youtu.be/ywVoaZ8d6iU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FywVoaZ8d6iU&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=dda29350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ywVoaZ8d6iU</a><br />\n抗議者に対する香港警察の残虐行為<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fSuhYcol7AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfSuhYcol7AE&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=7e36d1e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fSuhYcol7AE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/du-kvt_Yp0U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdu-kvt_Yp0U&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=03d3547e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/du-kvt_Yp0U</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GVqNN8t8sTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGVqNN8t8sTc&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=c093102f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GVqNN8t8sTc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LIP6aBrj_SY\" data-sr-url=\"ht