.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ffc69bjT3ROk&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=b5dd799e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fc69bjT3ROk</a><br />\n홍콩 경찰은 에스컬레이터에서 시민들을 밀고 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/ywVoaZ8d6iU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FywVoaZ8d6iU&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=dda29350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ywVoaZ8d6iU</a><br />\n시위대에 대한 홍콩 경찰의 폭력<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fSuhYcol7AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfSuhYcol7AE&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=7e36d1e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fSuhYcol7AE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/du-kvt_Yp0U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdu-kvt_Yp0U&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=03d3547e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/du-kvt_Yp0U</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GVqNN8t8sTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGVqNN8t8sTc&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=c093102f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GVqNN8t8sTc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LIP6aBrj_SY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLIP6aBrj_SY&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=a968a6f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LIP6aBrj_SY</a><br />\n도와주세요"},{"pid":"aa800c605e9c3683f8d866fed0f78b8003a0779d","tid":1756173,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:31:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">響理大外面唱「肥媽有話兒」既人同我入黎</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755724</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}